      <item>
        <title>born</title>
        <link>https://meorion.github.io/blog/fondulac/</link>
        <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jun 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://meorion.github.io/blog/fondulac/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;what does she remember? what has she forgotten? fuzz. lint on tongue. sharp angles. mother&amp;rsquo;s voice, like water on leaves. warmth filling her chest that she just now realized was empty. brushing her hair away from her face and around her ears. Her mother gently lowered her head, so her cheek now lay bare against the clean pillow. she would fall asleep. a face, like her own, looking back at her, eyes wide in a silent scream. she couldn&amp;rsquo;t hear anything. red ribbons flowing from her hands as mother ate the little girl&amp;rsquo;s fingers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      </item>
      
